WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.868 --> 00:00:03.770
Let's pretend
this is a safe space.

00:00:03.770 --> 00:00:05.772
Sharing intimate secrets
with coworkers can

00:00:05.772 --> 00:00:07.708
bond us together
and increase communication

00:00:07.708 --> 00:00:09.443
in the workplace.

00:00:09.443 --> 00:00:12.813
- Now, who wants to share first?

00:00:12.813 --> 00:00:14.047
 [gentle acoustic guitar]

00:00:14.047 --> 00:00:16.683
- I never admitted this before,
but...

00:00:16.683 --> 00:00:20.754
I hate my grandkids.
They just suck.

00:00:20.754 --> 00:00:24.291
- One time I hit a deer
with my car...

00:00:24.291 --> 00:00:25.659
because I wanted to.

00:00:25.659 --> 00:00:28.562
- Look, I am just gonna
say this: I am a cutter,

00:00:28.562 --> 00:00:30.864
and that works for me.

00:00:30.864 --> 00:00:32.032
- And that's when I realized

00:00:32.032 --> 00:00:37.504
I had inadvertently
helped do 9/11.

00:00:37.504 --> 00:00:38.805
- Beautiful.
- So, so great. Gorgeous.

00:00:38.805 --> 00:00:41.475
Let's all give Ted
a big round of applause

00:00:41.475 --> 00:00:45.712
and help him
feel supported.

00:00:45.712 --> 00:00:48.081
- Support Ted.

00:00:48.081 --> 00:00:50.384
Okay, seems like
everyone has shared.

00:00:50.384 --> 00:00:52.686
Except for you, Matt.

00:00:52.686 --> 00:00:56.089
Matt, why so shy?

00:00:56.089 --> 00:00:58.725
- Oh, yeah, I-I don't
really know if this is for me.

00:00:58.725 --> 00:01:00.394
I might just go for a swim.

00:01:00.394 --> 00:01:01.628
- Come on, Matt.
We've all shared

00:01:01.628 --> 00:01:04.498
with each other,
except for you.

00:01:04.498 --> 00:01:06.066
Just tell us something simple.
Be confident.

00:01:06.066 --> 00:01:09.002
Like, how did you lose
your virginity?

00:01:09.002 --> 00:01:11.838
- Oh. Uh...

00:01:11.838 --> 00:01:16.343
Okay.
Well, I was in college,

00:01:16.343 --> 00:01:19.846
and it was Halloween night,
and we were watching a movie.

00:01:19.846 --> 00:01:23.350
- Spooky. What movie?

00:01:23.350 --> 00:01:25.218
- I'd rather not say.

00:01:25.218 --> 00:01:27.321
both: Come on, come on.

00:01:27.321 --> 00:01:29.623
- It was "Hocus Pocus."

00:01:29.623 --> 00:01:31.625
- Excellent film.

00:01:31.625 --> 00:01:33.660
- Anyway, I got distracted
by the movie,

00:01:33.660 --> 00:01:34.795
and it lasted
way too long,

00:01:34.795 --> 00:01:37.531
and that's
the end of that story.

00:01:37.531 --> 00:01:39.967
- No, no, no, no.
It's not, Matt.

00:01:39.967 --> 00:01:41.835
We gotta go
way, way deeper.

00:01:41.835 --> 00:01:42.736
 [tribal flute trills]

00:01:42.736 --> 00:01:44.071
[deep voice] Way deeper.

00:01:44.071 --> 00:01:49.676
 ♪ ♪

00:01:49.676 --> 00:01:52.179
- I fully trust you
with my heart and mind

00:01:52.179 --> 00:01:54.648
to close-shave me
with a straight-edge razor.

00:01:54.648 --> 00:01:55.949
- I accept and honor
your trust

00:01:55.949 --> 00:01:58.218
and wish you
the very best of luck.

00:01:58.218 --> 00:01:59.486
- Well, look who's here.

00:01:59.486 --> 00:02:00.854
[knife slashes]
- Ow, my face.

00:02:00.854 --> 00:02:02.723
- Oh, sorry, Cliff,
but you moved.

00:02:02.723 --> 00:02:04.624
- Didn't think
you were the trust-shave,

00:02:04.624 --> 00:02:06.026
team-building type.

00:02:06.026 --> 00:02:07.661
- Oh, so you were
thinking about me.

00:02:07.661 --> 00:02:09.763
Now I have a personal tidbit
to put about you in

00:02:09.763 --> 00:02:11.999
my Excel spreadsheet:
"Thinks about Jake... A lot."

00:02:11.999 --> 00:02:15.235
- And I have something to put
about you in my Google Doc:

00:02:15.235 --> 00:02:19.172
"Suffers from narcissistic
personality disorder."

00:02:19.172 --> 00:02:20.440
Wanna get out of here?

00:02:20.440 --> 00:02:24.578
- Fine. Twist my arm.

00:02:24.578 --> 00:02:27.280
- Jake? [gasps]

00:02:27.280 --> 00:02:29.016
 [startling music]

00:02:29.016 --> 00:02:31.118
I fully trust you
with my heart and mind.

00:02:31.118 --> 00:02:34.821
- And then Bette Midler
sang a Broadway rendition

00:02:34.821 --> 00:02:37.924
of "I Put a Spell on You,"
and then I, uh--

00:02:37.924 --> 00:02:39.993
- Give it to us, Matt.
- Share, Matt.

00:02:39.993 --> 00:02:41.294
- I camed.

00:02:41.294 --> 00:02:43.663
[applause]

00:02:43.663 --> 00:02:46.166
- Good work, Matt.
Good work.

00:02:46.166 --> 00:02:47.868
- Give Matt a hug.
Show him some support.

00:02:47.868 --> 00:02:49.836
- Everybody touch his body.

00:02:49.836 --> 00:02:52.939
Wrap your arms around his neck
and love him.

